Date: Fri, 11 May 2012 14:06:43 -0400

 (and expr expr expr ...) means 2 mandatory expressions PLUS 0 or more expressions. 
 
 In general ANYTING ... means 0 or more of ANYTHING. 
 
 -- Matthias
 
 
 
